approaches_tried: Corner-based subset extraction from large N (N=50-200)
Adjacent N extraction (N+1 -> N by removing one tree)
findings: Corner-based and centroid-based extraction found NO improvements
Adjacent N extraction found 2 improvements (N=121 and N=122)
Improvement comes from extracting subsets from N=122 and N=123
notes: Subset extraction found 2 improvements by removing one tree from N+1 solutions. N=121 improved by 0.000766 (from N=122), N=122 improved by 0.000846 (from N=123). This is a novel approach that found improvements where local search methods failed.
